POCKETLEAK - PRIVACY POLICY

Last Updated: December 22, 2025

SIMPLE TRUTH: WE DO NOT COLLECT ANY DATA. PERIOD.

---

1. DATA COLLECTION

We do NOT collect any data from you. Zero. Nothing.

PocketLeak works 100% offline on your device. All your financial data stays on YOUR device only.

2. WHAT STAYS ON YOUR DEVICE

Your device stores:
- Your financial data (income, expenses, leaks, goals)
- Your profile settings
- Your app preferences

This data NEVER leaves your device unless YOU choose to:
- Sync to YOUR personal iCloud (optional)
- Export reports and share them yourself

3. NO SERVERS

We do NOT have servers. We do NOT store any user data. We CANNOT see your data.

Your data = Your device only.

4. NO TRACKING

We do NOT use:
- Analytics
- Tracking
- Cookies
- Third-party services
- Advertisement networks
- Data collection tools

5. NO DATA SHARING

We do NOT:
- Collect your data
- Share your data
- Sell your data
- Access your data
- Transmit your data anywhere

6. OFFLINE FIRST

PocketLeak works completely offline. No internet required to use the app.

Optional features:
- iCloud sync (syncs to YOUR iCloud only, controlled by YOU)
- In-app purchase (handled by Apple, we don't see payment info)

7. YOUR CONTROL

You have complete control:
- All data stored locally on YOUR device
- You can export your data anytime
- You can delete all data by deleting the app
- You control iCloud sync in iOS Settings

8. SECURITY

Your data is protected by:
- iOS encryption
- Face ID/Touch ID (if you enable it)
- iCloud encryption (if you use iCloud sync)

We don't handle security because we don't have your data.

9. IN-APP PURCHASES

We use Apple's StoreKit for the one-time purchase.
- Apple handles all payment processing
- We do NOT see your payment information
- We only verify purchase status locally on your device

10. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

PocketLeak is safe for all ages because we don't collect any data from anyone.

11. CHANGES TO POLICY

If we update this policy, we'll notify you in the app. But honestly, there's not much to change since we don't collect anything.

